	pro theo 1: testing the consequences

	pro theo 2: inverse the hypotheses (introduit la methode exploratoire du chapitre 7)

	The use of computer. (intro improved all module of our experimental science desription). For modeling : unsolvable analytical formalism (turing). New strategy to test and reverse-engineer with data (see Amonlirdviman, K. et al. Mathematical modeling of planar cell polarity to understand domineering nonautonomy. Science 307 for optimization of model parameters with automated (check that) data matching)

	....Computers can enhance each part of this simplistic experimental research workflow. bioemergences

	
